6281.title: Modern Family : Paris
6281.description: In one last family trip, they head to Paris so Jay can accept a lifetime achievement award in the closet industry, but his old nemesis, Earl Chambers, comes back to haunt him. Meanwhile, Claire has a secret rendezvous in one of the most romantic cities in the world, and Cam's lifelong dream of performing as Fizbo on the streets of Paris is about to become a reality
